{"tid":792347,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「人生必睇電影推介」- 四百擊 The 400 blows","createTime":"2018-08-24T13:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T10:46:24.000Z","uid":179096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94609e0b115a521b1aeda293d20f0724316ceb76","tid":792347,"uid":179096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/203723_702373600ade59817d4dedec01ecca79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F203723_702373600ade59817d4dedec01ecca79.png&h=6bb7d597&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/203724_8e0c7e6a25c0eae8f96c5ad4615404de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F203724_8e0c7e6a25c0eae8f96c5ad4615404de.png&h=01015b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年份：1959年 黑白<br />\n地區：法國<br />\n導演：杜魯福 Fran&ccedil;ois Truffaut<br />\n編輯：杜魯福 Fran&ccedil;ois Truffaut、Georges Charlot<br />\n演員：尚彼埃里奧 Jean-Pierre L&eacute;aud、克麗兒莫希雅、阿爾拔雷美<br />\n獎項：第12屆法國康城最佳導演<br />\n<br />\n好撚主觀非劇透推介原因：<br />\n<br />\n四百擊係法國新浪潮嘅先河電影之一，咁先簡單講下法國新浪潮背景。以前法國有本電影雜誌叫「電影手冊」，入面有班影評撚好撚睇唔過眼個陣時嘅荷李活濫製類型片風氣，而班撚樣決定用雜誌創辦人巴贊寫嘅法國新浪潮電影原則去拍屬於自已嘅電影，對抗班荷李活撚屌。<br />\n<br />\n四百擊入面唔可以唔撚提最後個running long shot，因為個個shot影響力到今時今日係全球好多部電影都會見到佢嘅影子，是但講兩套就例如黃進嘅「一念無明」同是枝裕和嘅「無人知曉的夏日清晨」<br />\n<br />\n係芸芸咁多套我稱之為「細路仔角度反抗大人世界電影系列」，好似「擦鞋童」、「鷹與男孩」、等等，但我最撚鐘意都係四百擊，可能因為我自已對長鏡頭有份情意結。"},{"pid":"bac18d62852ae937f552042e238baf831ecb89a9","tid":792347,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T22:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5b469415493799115bb7685f92c871c2abca41","tid":792347,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T22:30:11.000Z","msg":"好鬼得意 睇佢同佢個FD搞屎棍"},{"pid":"a303f2eafbc06bf878fc571ee6e1c74cdfe7645e","tid":792347,"uid":59322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"一念無明入面邊個shot？"}]}